    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>战略思维系列中文群：1018414610</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《战略思维：为自由而战》是一款二战历史驱动的回合制战略游戏。你将辗转欧洲、非洲和缅甸作战。你会在进攻前适当侦察，还是会大胆突进？你会借夜色和雨天的掩护偷偷接近敌军，还是只会抱怨天气不好？你会帮助当地人，还是会让他们自生自灭？你要担负重任，坚守欧洲民主自由的桥头堡，对抗轴心国的极权主义压迫。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/ac01555da4e4f7f83587e825fa720060.avif?t=1755021328\" width=616 height=115 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >从两种不同角度见证二战 </h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/33e018cee8aa45ed431baed88b54c297.poster.avif?t=1755021328\" width=596 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/33e018cee8aa45ed431baed88b54c297.webm?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/33e018cee8aa45ed431baed88b54c297.mp4?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏中有2个战役：英国战役完全由历史战斗组成，美国战役在击败德国之前是历史行动，之后还有一些对抗苏联的架空战斗。这是一个热爱二战历史，注重历史细节的团队的用心之作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/07977685ba1a7f9857eea276e8c93ed8.poster.avif?t=1755021328\" width=596 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/07977685ba1a7f9857eea276e8c93ed8.webm?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/07977685ba1a7f9857eea276e8c93ed8.mp4?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>作为哈罗德·亚历山大指挥英军</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从登陆挪威到解放意大利，指挥你的军队，忍受失败的痛苦，直到获得胜利。指挥敦刻尔克大撤退，在缅甸对抗日本人，在非洲对抗意大利人，在阿拉曼对抗德国人并反败为胜，结束北非的战事，然后在1943年胜利进军，登陆意大利。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/5782acf68aecf08593c1cb6a8e4591e8.poster.avif?t=1755021328\" width=596 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/5782acf68aecf08593c1cb6a8e4591e8.webm?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/5782acf68aecf08593c1cb6a8e4591e8.mp4?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>作为德怀特·艾森豪威尔指挥美军</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >从登陆日到攻克柏林，确保市场花园行动的成功，在阿登击败德国的最后反击，对帝国的心脏发动致命一击。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >再到1946年的架空历史，面对史上最强大的对手——红军。指挥美国和盟军部队，最小化损失，部署同盟国和被解放国家的所有军队，达到最大协同作用，用所有手段将民主自由带到东欧。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/bb54bfa58a72fffcb27a364abb643a42.poster.avif?t=1755021328\" width=596 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/bb54bfa58a72fffcb27a364abb643a42.webm?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/bb54bfa58a72fffcb27a364abb643a42.mp4?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >历史行动和架空场景</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>参与历史事件</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >确保你的所有部队能逃离敦刻尔克，完美指挥罗盘行动来告诉意大利人好好选择盟友，在第二次阿拉曼战役击败隆美尔以改变非洲的整个战局，于意大利重返欧洲，从诺曼底登陆开始一路攻向柏林，终结纳粹政权及其罪行。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/95700ee0761147ff2ef2c85e236e8d8e.avif?t=1755021328\" width=616 height=115 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>满足改变历史的好奇心</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >如果同盟国按照不可思议行动的计划，在1946年和苏联开战会怎么样？现在你可以作为指挥探索这种可能性，从共产主义手中解放东欧国家！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >会见高级官员</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏由剧情驱动，包含了很多历史人物，如温斯顿·丘吉尔、伯纳德·劳·蒙哥马利、富兰克林·德拉诺·罗斯福、德怀特·D·艾森豪威尔等等。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/4fa292f7db164c2842cbab99c056edf5.poster.avif?t=1755021328\" width=596 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/4fa292f7db164c2842cbab99c056edf5.webm?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/4fa292f7db164c2842cbab99c056edf5.mp4?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>让自己融入历史</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >体验剧情驱动的游戏过程，游戏中的行动穿插有大量历史人物的对话，他们的对话会被你的行为影响。在行动前后观看过场动画，深入体验1943年-1946年的事件。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/e4e7b46c40e9d204476a7e01ffc3b1e4.poster.avif?t=1755021328\" width=596 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/e4e7b46c40e9d204476a7e01ffc3b1e4.webm?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/e4e7b46c40e9d204476a7e01ffc3b1e4.mp4?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>管理军队</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >选择军队的编制，获得新单位、升级或解散落后的单位。游戏中有10种单位类型，每种都包含大量单位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/07dd1bf1db9002101a686b0c4b4eb193.poster.avif?t=1755021328\" width=596 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/07dd1bf1db9002101a686b0c4b4eb193.webm?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/07dd1bf1db9002101a686b0c4b4eb193.mp4?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>更新你的单位</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有新的单位可用时，马上获得它们。随着战役推进，你会在符合历史的时间点获得更先进的单位。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/e4b5f0aa94cf0ed5e98488e9ba7f7298.poster.avif?t=1755021328\" width=596 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/e4b5f0aa94cf0ed5e98488e9ba7f7298.webm?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/e4b5f0aa94cf0ed5e98488e9ba7f7298.mp4?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>为每次行动选择最好的装备</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >确保你的部队装备了下一场战斗所需的所有必需品。所有单位都能装备大量单位和载具。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/0594929ff27788ec0351b4073cbcb583.poster.avif?t=1755021328\" width=596 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/0594929ff27788ec0351b4073cbcb583.webm?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/0594929ff27788ec0351b4073cbcb583.mp4?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>训练你的部队并为其选择技能</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >监督部队作战，获得经验，为它们选择最符合你战略战术的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>指派英雄</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >指派英雄到指定的单位，获得特殊技能，所有的英雄都是历史人物。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>学习你的指挥部技能并使用先进战术</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在每次行动之前学习新的指挥部技能，用新学的知识影响战场。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/2e6478d474475a394d6423ec3c6aafff.poster.avif?t=1755021328\" width=596 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/2e6478d474475a394d6423ec3c6aafff.webm?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/2e6478d474475a394d6423ec3c6aafff.mp4?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>用敌军最强的单位对抗他们</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >夺取敌军最强的单位，用来装备你的部队，然后用敌军的力量碾碎他们。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/2adfced066969b7f6e9014533f7df5dc.poster.avif?t=1755021328\" width=596 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/2adfced066969b7f6e9014533f7df5dc.webm?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/2adfced066969b7f6e9014533f7df5dc.mp4?t=1755021328\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>体验真实的3D画质</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们研究了战斗地图，利用了3D画面的优势，有体积地形和单位移动的物理模拟。所有单位都细致再现了真实的模型。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/6eb29fbf80c7a42bf38239e0bf6430db.avif?t=1755021328\" width=616 height=115 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >欢迎游玩新作品</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《战略思维：为自由而战》是《战略思维》系列的第四部游戏，包含了英美的二战战役。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >系列前作：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《战略思维：太平洋》——第一部游戏，包含美国和日本在太平洋上的战斗。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《战略思维：闪电战》——第二部游戏，包含德国的二战战役。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《战略思维：共产主义的幽灵》——第三部游戏，包含苏联的二战战役。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1381850/extras/61ab33bfbc8f11aafae2631e4183a3ec.avif?t=1755021328\" width=616 height=115 /></span></p>",
